import PyPDF2

pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/2-HITs/HierarchyTransformers/paper.pdf'
reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(pdf_path)
num_pages = len(reader.pages)
text = ''
for i in range(min(num_pages, 10)):
    text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n'
print(text[:2000])
